  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2006-09-28",
    "date": "2006-10-24T21:42:25Z",
    "text": "Get Information on Financial Transactions Act - Amends title VI (International Education Programs) of the Higher Education Act of 1965 to direct the Secretary of Education to require, as part of the Integrated Postsecondary Education Data System (IPEDS) annual data collection, that each institution of higher education receiving federal funds for its international education programs include data concerning: (1) the total cost such a program or center; (2) state and private contributors whose total aggregate contributions exceed $100,000 for the fiscal year; and (3) the use of such contributions.\n\nDirects the Secretary to prepare an annual report summarizing such data."
  },
